{
  "texts": [
    "High-fidelity digital twin rendering DTN visualization requires support for different levels of detail in network element models and scenario models.",
    "Based on the specific application, an appropriate level of visualization fidelity should be chosen to construct a corresponding virtual environment.",
    "Visualization capabilities must encompass an entire network lifecycle from micro-scenarios to large-scale citylevel scenarios.",
    "This technology enables a high-fidelity representation of the actual network driven by digital threads.",
    "Network visualization can be modified using these digital threads, which results in dynamic visualization capabilities."
  ]
}